<!-- Phone Verification Modal -->
<div id="phoneVerificationModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
            <h3>Verificación de Seguridad</h3>
            <span class="close" onclick="closeModal('phoneVerificationModal')">&times;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <div id="phoneRequestStep" class="verification-step">
                <div class="verification-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="48" height="48">
                        <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <p>Para acceder a todas las transacciones, necesitamos verificar tu identidad.</p>
                <p>Enviaremos un código de verificación a tu teléfono registrado.</p>
                <div class="phone-display">
                    <strong>+34 ***-***-789</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="form-actions">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="closeModal('phoneVerificationModal')">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="sendVerificationCode()">Enviar Código</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="codeVerificationStep" class="verification-step" style="display: none;">
                <div class="verification-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="48" height="48">
                        <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"></path>
                        <path d="M21 12c-1 0-3-1-3-3s2-3 3-3 3 1 3 3-2 3-3 3"></path>
                        <path d="M3 12c1 0 3-1 3-3s-2-3-3-3-3 1-3 3 2 3 3 3"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <p>Hemos enviado un código de 6 dígitos a tu teléfono.</p>
                <p class="code-sent-message">Código enviado a +34 ***-***-789</p>
                
                <form id="verificationCodeForm">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="verificationCode">Introduce el código de verificación:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="verificationCode" maxlength="6" pattern="[0-9]{6}" placeholder="123456" required>
                        <small class="form-hint">El código expira en <span id="countdown">60</span> segundos</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-actions">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goBackToPhoneStep()">Volver</button>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Verificar</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
                
                <div class="resend-section">
                    <p>¿No has recibido el código?</p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-link" id="resendCodeBtn" onclick="resendVerificationCode()" disabled>
                        Reenviar código (<span id="resendCountdown">30</span>s)
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="verificationSuccessStep" class="verification-step" style="display: none;">
                <div class="verification-icon success">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="48" height="48">
                        <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                        <polyline points="22,4 12,14.01 9,11.01"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <p><strong>¡Verificación exitosa!</strong></p>
                <p>Ahora puedes acceder a todas tus transacciones.</p>
                <div class="form-actions">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="proceedToAllTransactions()">Continuar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
.verification-step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
}

.verification-icon {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #004481;
}

.verification-icon.success {
    color: #28a745;
}

.phone-display {
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-size: 18px;
}

.code-sent-message {
    color: #28a745;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

#verificationCode {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    padding: 15px;
    border: 2px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    width: 200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

#verificationCode:focus {
    border-color: #004481;
    outline: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 68, 129, 0.1);
}

.form-hint {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 14px;
}

.resend-section {
    margin-top: 30px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
}

.btn-link {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: #004481;
    text-decoration: underline;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
}

.btn-link:disabled {
    color: #999;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.btn-link:hover:not(:disabled) {
    color: #0056b3;
}

.countdown {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #dc3545;
}
</style>
